title: Anne Holt. Punishment
description:
A serial killer is on the loose in Norway. Abducting children and murdering them in
an undetectable way that confounds the police, he then returns the childs body 
to the mother with a note.You Got What You Deserved. Police superintendant Adam
Studo is the unlucky man in charge of the investigation.In desparation he recruits
former FBI profiler Johanne Vik to assist.
The killer has abducted three children, but one has not yet been returned to her
Mother. Is there a chance she is still alive.
